data.description: Welcome Home!  This fantastic, BETTER THAN NEW, 4 BR, 2.5 bath, 3/car gar. home, in desirable Wyndstone Estates is truly move-in ready!  In  last 2 yrs, sellers have taken pride of ownership & have added over $42,000 in upgrades inside & out.  Main fl. offers den w/ French doors, powder room w/updated hardware, fabulous great room with tons of natural lighting, open dining & spacious kitchen w/ center island, pendant lighting, quartz counters, tile backsplash, recessed & smart lighting, all new light fixtures, soft close cabinets & drawers, walk-in pantry & mud room w/bench seating. A true 3 car gar. equipped w/ 240V outlet for electric car. The 2nd story offers spacious primary w/large walk-in closet, dbl sinks, bath w/ custom enclosed glass shower door, 3 add'l BR;s, 1 w/ walk-in closet and convenient laundry room . Basement is dry, well insulated and ready for buyers to make it their own.  For peace of mind, seller has installed heavy duty sump pump with battery powered back-up.  Smart home products include: garage door opener, thermostat, doorbell and door handle.  This lot is over ½ acre and offers a fully sodded yard and irrigation system along with a low maintenance fenced-in privacy fence.  Get ready to LOVE WHERE YOU LIVE in this wonderful community.
